            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Nvim doesn't restore cursor position automatically. You need to set the cursor position to the `\"` mark to restore cursor position. `getpos('\"')` is not valid. To get the position of the `\"` mark you should use `getpos('''\"')` or `getpos(\"'\\\"\")`. `/tmp` is ignored from ShaDa as of 0.12.",
