            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "This is missing exact repro steps. \"nvim-lastplace plugin\" is irrelevant. \n\nThis sounds like you recently updated from Nvim 0.10 to 0.11, and presumably changed many other things, and have not tried `nvim --clean`.\n\nThis works for me on HEAD and 0.11.x:\n\n```\n  \" :help restore-cursor\n  autocmd BufReadPre * autocmd FileType <buffer> ++once\n    \\ if !&diff && &ft !~# 'commit\\|rebase' && line(\"'\\\"\") > 1 && line(\"'\\\"\") <= line(\"$\") | exe 'normal! g`\"' | endif\n```\n",
